{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-list-tsx","path":"/tags/Grafana/","result":{"data":{"allMdx":{"nodes":[{"excerpt":"新买了服务器果然能为自己创造一个又一个接连不断的需求。例如，笔者想到公网服务器上跑的定时脚本会把日志重定向到指定的文件里，但是并不会自动清理，意味着它们会在几十年后占满笔者的硬盘空间，这是不可接受不可妥协的！ 因此在本篇博客里，笔者计划部署统一的日志管理服务，存储来自各个地方的日志信息，既方便管理，也方便快速发现并修复问题。\n\n在 Github 上以  为关键词，按星标数排序…","fields":{"slug":"grafana-log-system"},"frontmatter":{"banner":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#181818","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b6199558d0d1ca4a552e386a9c211aab/d2c24/grafana-panel.png","srcSet":"/static/b6199558d0d1ca4a552e386a9c211aab/ad95d/grafana-panel.png 640w,\n/static/b6199558d0d1ca4a552e386a9c211aab/d5f71/grafana-panel.png 1280w,\n/static/b6199558d0d1ca4a552e386a9c211aab/d2c24/grafana-panel.png 2560w","sizes":"(min-width: 2560px) 2560px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/b6199558d0d1ca4a552e386a9c211aab/68d65/grafana-panel.webp 640w,\n/static/b6199558d0d1ca4a552e386a9c211aab/4c779/grafana-panel.webp 1280w,\n/static/b6199558d0d1ca4a552e386a9c211aab/c4165/grafana-panel.webp 2560w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 2560px) 2560px, 100vw"}]},"width":2560,"height":1227}}},"categories":["技术琐事"],"tags":["Grafana","Loki","Alloy","Docker"],"title":"通过 Grafana 管理日志信息","date":"2025-06-03T00:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-06-12T00:00:00.000Z","timeliness":null}}]}},"pageContext":{"ids":["dc922807-1f0b-54c3-9391-b30c0b7d983d"],"tag":"Grafana"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2291570122","2940271172"],"slicesMap":{}}